EL approved IVA on 27/04/2023. Glycogen Storage Disease, Type II(GSD2) – Autosomal Recessive. Note-
The pathogenic classification for this variant is only for when it is in cis with c.752C>T. This variant alone has not been seen, as far as I know, in an affected individual or to affect the protein function by itself.

A third pathogenic variant, c.1411_1414del, is often found in cis with c.[752C>T; 761C>T].
